long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Facebook groups data from the groups search page to a XLS/CSV file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open a Facebook groups search page and search.
2️⃣ Click the Download Groups List button.     
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:

1️⃣ Running solely on your local machine, no need to worry about any privacy concerns, all data remains on your local device.
2️⃣ Export groups data to a xls/csv file, data include: Group Id, Group Name, Group Url, Has Membership Questions, Viewer Forum Join State, Viewer Join State, Group Profile Image Url, Type And Members, Group Description, Origin Search Url.

🎯 Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your business data management and make informed decisions with Facebook Groups Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Facebook❗️🔒
